        "title": "Sort array after deleting value",
        "body": "<p>how can I sort an Array after deleting one value?<\/p>\n\n<p>e.g. <code>{1,2,3,4,5}<\/code> --> <code>{1,2,null,4,5}<\/code> --> <code>{1,2,4,5,null}<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public boolean removeNumber(int accountNumber) {\n    for(int i = 0; i &lt; Account.length; i++) {\n        if(Account[i].getAccountNumber() == (accountNumber)) {\n            Account[i] = null;\n        }\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
